text: Bought kopi o kosong here at $1.30. I added milk powder to my kopi o kosong. The body is averagely ok, the flavor is averagely ok also. The price is on the higher side.

I have been to so many coffeeshops around Tampines, this is the WORSE place for coffee. Kopi-O Kosong (black coffee without milk or sugar) for S$1.30??? That's ridiculous. Cut throat prices. This is heartland area with many old retired folks. Food wise is ok. Don't buy drinks from the drink stall....
